<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/2412?language=en' lang='en'>
How we can make crops survive without water
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Jan 2016
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
