<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='783600' id='t-783600'>when they dry out.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='785280' id='t-785280'>All modern crops, therefore,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='787080' id='t-787080'>have these genes
in their roots and leaves,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='789160' id='t-789160'>they just never switch them on.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='790920' id='t-790920'>They only switch them on in seed tissues.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:24
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='793440' id='t-793440'>So what we're trying to do right now</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='795200' id='t-795200'>is to understand the environmental
and cellular signals</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='797840' id='t-797840'>that switch on these genes
in resurrection plants,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='801280' id='t-801280'>to mimic the process in crops.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:34
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='803680' id='t-803680'>And just a final thought.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='805440' id='t-805440'>What we're trying to do very rapidly</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='807680' id='t-807680'>is to repeat what nature did
in the evolution of resurrection plants</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='811520' id='t-811520'>some 10 to 40 million years ago.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:45
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='814160' id='t-814160'>My plants and I thank you
for your attention.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:47
</data>
